2009年，商台公信力居於全港傳媒的第三位<ref>{{cite news | language =  | author =  | coauthors =  | url = http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/091005/4/ejqb.html | title = 傳媒公信力調查報告 | work =  | publisher = 明報 | pages =  | date = 2009-10-06 | accessdate =  | archive-date = 2010-04-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100419193739/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/091005/4/ejqb.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，旗下的頻道[[雷霆881|雷霆881商業一台]]是香港聽眾人數最多的電台。<ref>{{cite web | language =  | publisher =  | title = 881903.com - 關於商台 | url = http://www.881903.com/Page/FooterHTML/About_CR_c.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2009-11-20 | archive-date = 2012-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120518033840/http://www.881903.com/Page/FooterHTML/About_CR_c.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。

=== 2010年代 ===
